SHEET
DETERMINATION METHOD: DSSP
THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "AF" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN  8-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
A  9-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.

THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "BE" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN  8-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
A  9-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.
